parameters.toolDescription:
MemoryClaw memory tools. Use the userId provided in the user message.

Parameters for each tool:
  - memory_search: {"query": "string", "userId": "<userId from message>"}
  - memory_add:    {"message": "string", "userId": "<userId from message>"}
  - memory_get:    {"path": "string", "userId": "<userId from message>"}
  - memory_delete: {"path": "string", "userId": "<userId from message>"}

Always read the userId from the message context and pass it to every tool call.
